  <brief_title>Impact of Systematic Tracking of Dementia Cases on the Rate of Hospitalization in Emergency Care Units</brief_title>
  <acronym>IDEM</acronym>
  <official_title>Interest of Systematic Tracking of Dementia Cases in Nursing Homes: Analysing the Contribution of MultiDisciplinary Team Meeting (MDTM) in Alzheimer's Disease and Related Diseases</official_title>
  <sponsors>
